    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      185.17,
      512.98,
      212.25
    ],
    "text": "Properties Suspected to Have Been Acquired Using Proceeds of Drug Trafficking Frozen \u2013 Unlawful Assets Investigation Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      226.81,
      540.34,
      267.72
    ],
    "text": "The Unlawful Assets Investigation Division has launched an investigation following information received regarding a woman residing in Kelanimulla North, Angoda, who is suspected of having acquired assets through the proceeds of drug trafficking.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      282.16,
      541.64,
      323.04
    ],
    "text": "Investigations revealed that two three-wheelers, valued at approximately Rs. 2 million, had been registered in the names of the suspect and one of her close associates. In addition, a bus valued at approximately Rs. 3 million had been registered in the name of the suspect's son.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      337.6,
      544.78,
      378.48
    ],
    "text": "After presenting the relevant facts before the Aluthkade Magistrate's Court No. 08 on 08.07.2026, the court issued an order to freeze the aforementioned assets until 14.07.2026, pending the completion of further investigations.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      393.04,
      507.94,
      406.32
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being conducted by the Unlawful Assets Investigation Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
